desmoj.extensions.visualization2d.animation.core.simulator

Class ModelAnimation

  • java.lang.Object
    • desmoj.core.simulator.NamedObject
      • desmoj.core.simulator.ModelComponent
        • desmoj.core.simulator.Reportable
          • desmoj.core.simulator.Model
            • desmoj.extensions.visualization2d.animation.core.simulator.ModelAnimation

  • public abstract class ModelAnimation
extends Model
    Animated version of model. ModelAnimation extends Model about a CmdGeneration instance and a showInAnimation switch. A animated model must extend form ModelAnimation.

    • Constructor Detail

      • ModelAnimation

        public ModelAnimation(ModelAnimation owner,
                      java.lang.String name,
                      CmdGeneration cmdGen,
                      boolean showInReport,
                      boolean showInTrace,
                      boolean showInAnimation)
        ModelAnimation extends Model about a CmdGeneration instance and a showInAnimation switch. In constructor you must define: setModelAuthor(..), setModelDate(), addRemark(), addIcon() and setGeneratedBy()
        Parameters:
        owner - supermodel, may be null
        name - name of model
        cmdGen - CmdGeneration object
        showInReport - switch for report generation
        showInTrace - switch for trace generation
        showInAnimation - switch for cmds-file generation
